<plot>Summer is an aging adult entertainer who has just discovered that an affair with a client has led to her becoming pregnant. Because of the client's married status (and her own drug addiction) Summer believes that the only way out of the situation is an abortion. On the eve of the event however, Summer meets Sienna-the younger deaf sister of a rival entertainer (Lacie) at the club where she works. Throughout the course of the night, pressure from her baby's father, her predatory boss, and her own addiction push Summer into a place where she finally acknowledges her maternal instincts and force her to reconsider a decision she thought she already made.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?505473</url></doc>
